            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded species_image_contain">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Get in touch with Tanya</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>If you’d like to get in touch with Tanya, one of our expert or policy specialists, or another&nbsp;of our generalist&nbsp;spokespeople, please contact the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/press-centre/press-contacts">press team</a>.</p>
<p>You can also follow&nbsp;Tanya on Twitter:&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/TanyaMSteele">@TanyaMSteele</a></p>


      </div>
          </div>
</section>


