            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>As well as our trustees, we also benefit from the valuable expertise of external advisors on our Impact Goals Committee, Investments Committee and Nomination &amp; Remuneration Committee. Our Scottish and Welsh operations also benefit from the insight of our Scottish Council and Welsh Council.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>


